ANIMA ECLIPTICA — Sacred Small Circle (Sunday 23. November, Berlin)

A night for those who feel the call.
Shadow. Light. Truth.
A living theatre where your inner self becomes visible.

This is not a public event.
It is a protected circle, limited seats, intimate, guided with deep presence and Hands of Light.
Only for those truly ready to step into their inner portal.

Reservation is required.

The Kharmel Cochrane casting team are seeking real American and Canadian men based in the UK and Europe for a feature film: 3*0s - 60s, Male, Open on Ethnicity*

**Filming: **16th March - 1st June 2026 *(subject to change)*

**Talent must be based in the UK / Europe.**

**We’re especially interested in hearing from American men with interesting features and unique, haunting faces.**

No previous acting experience required. Paid opportunity.

To apply, email **selfie@kharmelcochrane.co.uk**

with the subject “Feature Film - US / Canadian Man”.

Please include full name, age, location, selfie and short introduction.

Kharmel Cochrane Casting: [https://kharmelcochrane.com](https://kharmelcochrane.com/)

items.text:
🎉Actors’ Jingle & Mingle Networking Party!✨

Hey there fellow actors!

If you’re living in Beds, Bucks, or Herts (or anywhere close enough to hop on over) come Mingle & Jingle with us at the Ultimate Holiday Actors Networking Party! 🎭🎁 

(This party is supported by Equity but you don't have to be an Equity member to come!)

Meet other local actors in a festive night of networking, connecting, and sharing. Whether you’re a seasoned pro or just starting out, this event is for you!

Ho ho holy crap! Get a free drink and party and get your photo taken with The Real Santa -what!? 🎅📸

Tickets are free and limited — grab yours now and join our growing local acting community! 🌟

❄ Event Details

• Friday 5 December

• 7pm–11pm

• Leighton Buzzard Library Theatre – Lounge

• Equity-supported event (you do not need to be a member)

🎁 How to Join

Book your ticket here:

https://www.tickettailor.com/events/offstageacting/1960884

• Fill out the quick form

• Share with your actor friends 🎭

• Bring the ticket on your phone

• Walk in, grab your free drink, and start mingling! 🍸✨

Looking forward to seeing everyone on December 5th! ☃ 

The perfect way to kick off the holiday season! 🎄

items.text:
Casting Call 🎉🎉🎉

‘The Lines We Crossed’ short film 🎬

A raw and tender story of found family, the messiness of healing, and the unexpected power of being seen. Three lives, stitched together by loneliness, come alive in the light of connection - and in that light, hope can take root where none was meant to grow.

Secondary role: 
Mrs. Kane is dramatic, flirty, and unapologetically over-the-top, with a flair for gossip and a love of all things a little chavvy. While she loves both of her children, her eldest, Cody, is clearly the favorite - her pride and joy - often leaving Keira to fend for herself. Mrs. Kane desperately clings to Cody’s success, seeing it as her ticket to status and financial security.

• Female
• 30-55 years
• White/Caucasian
• Brunette/ Redhead/ Auburn hair
• London Accent

📍Location: London
🗓️ Dates: 6/12/25
💰 Payment: Unpaid
✨ Great opportunity for actors looking to gain experience, showreel material, and festival exposure.

⚠️ Deadline to apply: 28/11

To audition please contact @lines_we_crossed_film on instagram or send Madeleine Bloore a message here on Facebook. 

We can’t wait to hear from you 😉

✨👑 Calling all performers! 👑✨
Do you dream of becoming a princess?
Lulu’s Magical Moments is casting Northamptonshire princess performers who can bring sparkle, energy, and magical improv skills to every event!

If you love performing, creating unforgettable moments, and spreading fairytale magic, we want to hear from you!
✨ Must drive
✨ Must love improvising
✨ Must bring BIG princess energy

Email lulusmagicalmoments@outlook.com to apply! 💖👑✨

**CASTING CALL: LIVE SHOW HOSTS**

Los Angeles (Hollywood Studio)

**Firework** is seeking energetic, camera-ready **Live Show Hosts** to lead interactive livestream product demonstrations!

**PAY:** $25-$40/hour (based on experience)

**ROLE DETAILS:**
* Host live product shows from our Hollywood, CA studio
* Present tech & lifestyle products in an authentic, conversational style
* Work as freelance/1099 with potential to transition to part-time employee
* Average 5-10 hours/week (rarely exceeds 15 hours)
* Mostly weekdays, 8 AM - 8 PM PT

**WE'RE LOOKING FOR:**
* Strong on-camera presence & natural speaking ability
* Reliable, punctual, professional
* Available weekdays during business hours
* Prior hosting/livestream/UGC/acting experience preferred but not required

**AUDITION OPTIONS:**

**Option 1: On-Site Audition**
* Dates: December 10-11, 2025
* Time: 10 AM - 1 PM PT
* 10-15 min audition (3-min one-take hosting scenario)

**Option 2: Self-Tape Submission**
* Deadline: December 11, 2025 (11:59 PM PT)
* 3 minutes, vertical, one continuous take
* Host any tech/electronic product as if live
* Email to: Kimmy@fireworkhq.com
* Subject: [Your Name] – Live Show Host Submission - LA Digital Showroom Host - Self Tape Submission

**TO APPLY:** [https://jobs.lever.co/fireworkhq/cd7d4561-4c57-4260-b880-8000a95f6f44](https://jobs.lever.co/fireworkhq/cd7d4561-4c57-4260-b880-8000a95f6f44)

**Questions? **Contact: [Kimmy@fireworkhq.com](mailto:Kimmy@fireworkhq.com)

items.text:
Now casting couples in mixed orientation relationships for a new documentary series with a major cable network.

Mixed orientation relationships, often known as lavender partnerships, involve two partners who differ in their sexual orientation. We want to hear from couples who live together, share a daily life, and are engaged, married, or soon to be engaged.

This series will explore how couples navigate identity, commitment, outside expectations, and the realities of loving in a way that challenges societal norms.

If this describes you or someone you know, you can share your story at the link below.

mixedorientationcasting.castingcrane.com

We are looking for couples who: •Identify as mixed orientation Live together and share daily life •Engaged, Married, Or Soon To Be Engaged This series will explore how couples balance love, identity, outside expectations, and the realities of a relationship that goes against societal norms. SHARE YOUR STORY castingebodegapictures.com mixedorintotons.sing.'

items.text:
2 DATS LEFT RSVP --->  https://forms.gle/GhutENbwc6vpXBLm9

We are giving rising talent their flowers. The Viral Stars & Honors Soirée is coming, and we are celebrating actors and digital creators who didn’t just go viral, but made real impact with 100K+ views and performances people could not scroll past.

This is not a regular industry mixer. It is a night of recognition, community, and opportunity with creators, actors, directors, casting contacts, marketing professionals, and digital storytellers all in one room. Expect real networking, genuine connection, a talent honors presentation, light bites, refreshments, karaoke, crystal giveaways, and the option to stay for a discounted murder mystery experience after 4 PM.

If you are looking to enter acting, grow as a creator, expand your network, or finally step into spaces that can open doors, this is your sign to show up.

Sunday, Nov 30 | 2–6 PM
Business Cocktail Attire
RSVP Required
Link in bio or QR code on flyer

The next wave of talent is being recognized. The next wave of opportunity is happening in the room. Be there.

Official Hashtags: #ViralStarsSoiree #honoredbyflink #flinksoiree

#IndustryMixer #DigitalCreators #ActorsCommunity #ContentCreators #HoustonEvents #HoustonCreators #EntertainmentIndustry #TalentShowcase #NetworkingEvent

2 DAYS LEFT TO RSVP---> QR Code & LINK Below - YOU'RE INVITED THIS SUNDAY 🥂Celebrating the contributions of our actors and networking with other industry peers – Flink Appreciation Event, November 30th @3pm (WestChase)

We’re officially in countdown mode—only 2 days left to RSVP for the Viral Stars & Honors Soirée. We don’t want you to miss it, and we are finalizing our headcount, food, gifts, and seating now.

We're opening registration, and you're invited! Take a quick minute today to secure your spot using the link below:

RSVP Link: PAUSE QR CODE https://forms.gle/GhutENbwc6vpXBLm9

Bringing a friend or inviting a peer? Make sure they register as well. Every attendee needs their own RSVP so we can prepare properly and make sure everyone has the full experience.

We are celebrating viral talent that has surpassed 100K+ views and bringing together creators, performers, directors, casting professionals, and industry players for a night of connection and inspiration.

If you need help registering or want the link sent directly, just reply :

sydneejane@flinkbrandcoach.com #flinkhonors #flinkhouston #flinkusa #flinksoiree

items.summary:
2 DATS LEFT RSVP --->  https://forms.gle/GhutENbwc6vpXBLm9

We are giving rising talent their flowers. The Viral Stars & Honors Soirée is coming, and we are celebrating actors and digital creators who didn’t just go viral, but made real impact with 100K+ views and performances people could not scroll past.

This is not a regular industry mixer. It is a night of recognition, community, and opportunity with creators, actors, directors, casting contacts, marketing professionals, and digital storytellers all in one room. Expect real networking, genuine connection, a talent honors presentation, light bites, refreshments, karaoke, crystal giveaways, and the option to stay for a discounted murder mystery experience after 4 PM.

If you are looking to enter acting, grow as a creator, expand your network, or finally step into spaces that can open doors, this is your sign to show up.

Sunday, Nov 30 | 2–6 PM
Business Cocktail Attire
RSVP Required
Link in bio or QR code on flyer

The next wave of talent is being recognized. The next wave of opportunity is happening in the room. Be there.

Official Hashtags: #ViralStarsSoiree #honoredbyflink #flinksoiree

DAHLONEGA- Short Film- Auditions Open! 
Local Talent!
Unpaid-IMDB credited

Auditions happen NOW! for the first film of the season: “THE SHAPE OF GOODBYE”

DEADLINE: Jan. 4th

An adaptation of the amazing play written by the talented John Mabey. 

All you have to do is email a video link of a 1-2 minute dramatic monologue to

fofingerfilmsauditions@gmail.com

Here is the Character list: 

MARCUS (30-45) stoic, disciplined, carrying unspoken grief
YOUNG MARCUS (17-21)- introspective, sensitive, with a youthful vulnerability
DUSTIN (45-60) - strong, confident, with a commanding presence
BOYFRIEND (17-21) - charming, caring, with a playful yet earnest demeanor
 HUSBAND (30-45) - loyal, contlicted, balancing love and responsibility
 MOTHER (35-45) - nurturing, resilient, emotionally grounded

Film summary 
THE SHAPE OF GOODBYE: 
FOLLOWS A FATHER AND SON
AS THEY STRUGGLE TO CONNECT
OF IN THEIR FRACTURED RELATIONSHIP ACROSS TIME. THROUGH GRIEF, LOVE AND HUMOR, THEY FIGHT THEIR WAY TOWARD HEALING AND TO EACH OTHER. AND WHAT THEY DISCOVER ALONG THE WAY FRACTURES
THE SHAPE OF TIME ITSELF AS MEMORIES
BECOME MANIFEST AND REVEAL UNSPOKEN TRUTHS.

FILMING DATES:

JAN. 31,FEB. 1st, and FEB, 7th and 8th
(subject to change)

WHERE: 
DAHLONEGA, GA

NON-PAID, IMDb CREDIT INCLUDED

Good luck! Message if you have any questions. We will gladly help you!

FO FINGER FILMS.

items.text:
Role Type: Supporting Gender: Male Age Range: Early to mid-20s Ethnicity: African American Build: Tall, physically imposing preferred

 Character Description:

 Dre is loud, cocky, and always looking to prove himself — even when no one’s watching. He’s the type to stir the pot just for the reaction. A natural bully with a chip on his shoulder, Gangster Type. He’s a knucklehead with presence — the guy you hear before you see. Seeking an actor with strong physicality and comedic or dramatic timing to bring Dre’s over-the-top bravado to life.

GRANDMA B Role Type: Supporting / Featured Gender: Female Age Range: Late 60s to 70s Ethnicity: African American, Mixed Race, or Hispanic Build: Average height and build.

 Character Description:

 Grandma B is the rock of the family — wise, resilient, and sharp as ever. She speaks her mind with no filter and delivers truth with wit and love. Strong in her faith and unshakable in her values, she’s as quick with a Bible verse as she is with a one-liner. Whether offering tough love or quiet comfort, she’s always ten steps ahead. Looking for a seasoned actress who can bring warmth, sass, and soul to this memorable matriarch. 

 Roylina

Female25-40 y.o.

Latino / Hispanic

Character Description: 

Roylina is a powerful Mafia Boss—commanding, strategic, and captivating. She carries herself with confidence, intensity, and an air of danger. The actress must be able to portray strength, authority, and emotional depth.

JACOB (JAY) -

Type: Principal

Gender: Male

Age Range: Early to mid-20s

Ethnicity: African American or Mixed Race

Complexion: Brown to Light

Build: Tall, athletic

 

Character Description:

Jacob (Jay) is confident, grounded, and carries a quiet strength. He’s sharp, emotionally mature beyond his years, and physically active. Jay’s presence is felt even in silence – calm but commanding. His past has shaped him, but he doesn’t wear it on his sleeve. Looking for an actor who can bring both vulnerability and strength to the role with authenticity and nuance.

sharedPost.text:
Der Kino Mittwoch auf radioYpsilon 

MOVIETIME KW 48/2025

ALLTAG EINER EHE UND DER ANIMATIONSHIT DES JAHRES

9 Jahre ist es her, nun ermitteln Judy Hopps und Nick Wilde erneut  in ZOOMANIA 2 (Stadtkinocenter Laa,  Babylon Kino Horn und Filmbühne Waidhofen/Ybbs).

Den Alltag eines Ehepaares nach vielen gemeinsamen Beziehungsjahren bringt uns Neele Leana Vollmar empathisch auf die Leinwand. So nebenbei durften wir auch mit der Regisseurin ein paar Worte wechseln.

Ausserdem gibt es noch eine Doppelconferance im Interview mit Cynthia Erivo und Ariana Grande sowie erzählt uns Rick Kavanian über die Arbeit als Synchronsprecher zum neuesten Disney Zeichentrick Blockbuster.

Weitere Filmtipps wie zb aus dem Kronenkino Mistelbach und Musik aus 80 Jahren Moviehistory präsentiert Ihnen Sarah Fuchs. 

Mittwoch 26.11.25 von 18 bis 19h auf radioYpsilon 94.5 oder via Stream (http://mp3.radioypsilon.at:8000/)

**AUSDRUCKSSTARKE PEOPLE-MODELS FÜR FOTOSHOOTING IN KREFELD GESUCHT **

​

Für ein Fotoshooting am 13.01.2024 für die Homepage eines Augenzentrums suchen wir vier ausdrucksstarke People-Models oder Darsteller.

​

Das Shooting findet in Krefeld statt und wir voraussichtlich 8 Stunden dauern. Ein Makeup-Artist wird vor Ort sein. 

​

Die Tagesgage beträgt 300,00€, die Abrechnung erfolgt auf Rechnung.

​

Weitere Infos unter folgendem Link https://www.castfinder-casting.de/shooting-krefeld

​

Wir freuen uns auf Eure Bewerbungen!

​

​

PS: Für Jobangebote schau mal hier vorbei: https://www.facebook.com/groups/castfinder.de

Und hier gibt‘s Jobangebote sowie Casting- und Schauspieltipps: https://www.instagram.com/castfinder_casting_coaching/

items.text:
# EXCITING WEEKEND AHEAD

We’re holding our final casting session for the main roles in Got to Be Certain. The shortlist is full of fantastic actors, and it’s going to be tough to make the final selections.

This project has been a joy to shape, and we can’t wait to see these performances bring the story to life. Stay tuned for updates - big things are coming!

There's still a chance to be part of this exciting project. A Casting Call is open until 31st December for some of the support roles in the film. Please see the images attached to this post. To apply, please email **doublesixproductionsltd@gmail.com** with your details and the role for which you would like to apply.

NOTE: You must be based in the North West of England, preferably Lancashire, as filming takes place in Chorley and the surrounding areas.

Follow us on instagram: [https://instagram/doublesixproductions.ig](https://instagram/doublesixproductions.ig)

Get in the mood by listening to the soundtrack on Amazon Music (no subscription required) [https://music.amazon.co.uk/user-playlists/a51a2af0e4ae4943b5b234ad97728018engb?marketplaceId=A1F83G8C2ARO7P&musicTerritory=GB&ref=dm_sh_VN1CdGRSfm1f4tWYxwk7ABpy5](https://music.amazon.co.uk/user-playlists/a51a2af0e4ae4943b5b234ad97728018engb?marketplaceId=A1F83G8C2ARO7P&musicTerritory=GB&ref=dm_sh_VN1CdGRSfm1f4tWYxwk7ABpy5)

The Kharmel Cochrane casting team are seeking real American and Canadian men based in the UK and Europe for a feature film: 3*0s - 60s, Male, Open on Ethnicity*

**Filming: **16th March - 1st June 2026 *(subject to change)*

**Talent must be based in the UK / Europe.**

**We’re especially interested in hearing from American men with interesting features and unique, haunting faces.**

No previous acting experience required. Paid opportunity.

To apply, email **selfie@kharmelcochrane.co.uk**

with the subject “Feature Film - US / Canadian Man”.

Please include full name, age, location, selfie and short introduction.

Kharmel Cochrane Casting: [https://kharmelcochrane.com](https://kharmelcochrane.com/)

To celebrate the launch of my brand-new book The Trinity Acting Method, I’m running the biggest acting competition I’ve ever created — and to enter, you MUST pre-order the book.
🎁 Pre-order the book here:�👉 https://amzn.to/485NUPi�(These are standard copies — NOT signed. Signed copies ONLY go to winners.)

🥇 1st Place — Prize Value: Over £1,000
* 1 YEAR of MZA training (in-person or online, includes subscribed members)
* A signed & personalised copy of The Trinity Acting Method (posted)
* A guaranteed acting role in MZA’s 2026 Vertical Drama Series Production

* A signed copy of The Trinity Acting Method (posted)

* What your research shows about what makes The Trinity Acting Method stand out
* Why you’re excited to read it

Your video MUST be public so it can be seen.

* Entries close: 31 January 2025

🎉Actors’ Jingle & Mingle Networking Party!✨

Hey there fellow actors!

If you’re living in Beds, Bucks, or Herts (or anywhere close enough to hop on over) come Mingle & Jingle with us at the Ultimate Holiday Actors Networking Party! 🎭🎁 

(This party is supported by Equity but you don't have to be an Equity member to come!)

Meet other local actors in a festive night of networking, connecting, and sharing. Whether you’re a seasoned pro or just starting out, this event is for you!

Ho ho holy crap! Get a free drink and party and get your photo taken with The Real Santa -what!? 🎅📸

Tickets are free and limited — grab yours now and join our growing local acting community! 🌟

❄ Event Details

• Friday 5 December

• 7pm–11pm

• Leighton Buzzard Library Theatre – Lounge

• Equity-supported event (you do not need to be a member)

🎁 How to Join

Book your ticket here:

https://www.tickettailor.com/events/offstageacting/1960884

• Fill out the quick form

• Share with your actor friends 🎭

• Bring the ticket on your phone

• Walk in, grab your free drink, and start mingling! 🍸✨

Looking forward to seeing everyone on December 5th! ☃ 

The perfect way to kick off the holiday season! 🎄

sharedPost.text:
We have had many success stories over the years. Here are a few examples from students attending our courses. 

- Billie May Verity attended our Emmerdale course and was cast as Beth's auntie in Emmerdale.
- Amy Jo Clough attended a Hollyoaks course and was cast as Cassie.
- Josh Clayton auditioned for a featured role in Emmerdale and reached the final two candidates.
- Chrissy Parle attended the Kate Bone course and was cast in the BBC's The Responder. 

Our next adult acting course is a 4 week course for actors age 16+. In the final week, the actors will perform in a mock casting in front of Award winning Hollyoaks Casting Director Peter Hunt. Peter will give feedback, notes and direction on each individual performance.

 We have had a great success rate from previous Hollyoak's Courses. 

The fee is £145

Studio 96, Salford, Media City, M50 2GZ

if you would like to book your place please click the link below:

https://screenplayacting.com/product/hollyoaks-course-january-2026/

🕊️ Reviving The Islamic Spirit (RIS) Convention 2025
📍 Trade Only
🗓️ December 19 — 21, 2025

Join thousands at this year’s RIS Convention, celebrating 24 years of Reviving the Spirits. Experience spiritually centered sessions that nurture the heart in the morning, interactive and thought-provoking discussions in the afternoon, and inspiring power talks in the evening that uplift the soul.

Make your RIS journey peaceful, seamless, and comfortable with Luxury Black Car Service — Toronto’s trusted provider for family, group, and event transportation.

🚘 Arrive With Peace. Travel With Comfort.

✨ Our Executive Chauffeur Services:

Point-to-Point Convention Transfers

Hourly Chauffeur Service for full-day attendance

Airport Pickups (YYZ, YTZ)

Hotel ↔ MTCC Transfers

Family & Group Transportation

Luxury SUVs and Sedans for a calm, relaxed ride

Focus on reflection, gathering knowledge, and spiritual growth.
We’ll take care of the travel — smoothly and on time.

📲 Text / WhatsApp: (905) 276-7676
📞 Call: (905) 276-7676

#LuxuryBlackCarService #TorontoLimo #YYZLimo

Figyelem jövendőbeli modellek!

December 7.-én MODELL WORKSHOP 
kerül megszervezésre Budapesten!

Szervezők: 

Tomolik Balázs- nemzetközi divatmodell.

A workshop alatt a modell szakmai rejtelmeit segít elsajátítani, a helyes kéztartásoktól kezdve a pózolási technikákon át a szemkontaktusig.

Nagy Zoltán– művészeti vezető és fotográfus, aki a modell portfóilódat készíti a workshop alatt. Számos divatmagazinnak készített fotókat, profi modellekkel.

Bővebb információ: 

http://www.magnet-mplay.hu/modell2025/?fbclid=PAT01DUAOS5MtleHRuA2FlbQIxMABzcnRjBmFwcF9pZA81NjcwNjczNDMzNTI0MjcAAacz2ob686Pvv-0xrxIIKsNUbFI214BHhbxbzIgZeBnio_MiGfj9ZXywZ4NOng_aem_W-pz5eoEbI9Mqo7sxZ3KeA

Jegyek: 
https://cooltix.hu/event/6921a6db12dc29b80729614c

Amit tartalmaz: 
- Nemzetközi kapcsolatok építése(külföldre való utazás lehtősége, divatmárkákkal való együtt dolgozás)
- Modell pózok (kéz/láb tartások, szemkontaktus) tanulása, 3 órán keresztül 
- Model séta betanítása
- Profi portfólió készítés, bővítés, profi fotóssal

Ott találkozunk!🤙🤟

🎬 CASTING – NOWY PROGRAM TV (Warszawa i okolice)

Szukamy osób do scen interwencji policyjnych w nowym programie telewizyjnym!

📅 Nagrania: 9–12 grudnia 2025
🎥 Wszystkie role: max pół dnia zdjęciowego
💰 Stawki: 400–500 zł netto

🔥 ROLE SZUKANE NA 9–10 grudnia

(nagranie dla każdej roli będzie 1 dzień z podanych – w trakcie ustaleń)

🚗 Wiktor Malinowski (30) – właściciel samochodu – 500 zł
💍 Julia Malinowska (30) – żona Wiktora – 500 zł

items.text:
Hello all,

I'm new to this group, just thought I'd introduce myself - I am a location sound recordist with almost a decade of experience, with bases in Somerset and Surrey as well as an extensive list of professional equipment. I'm currently free until about mid-Spring next year.

I am currently hoping to offer my services for a particular type of short fan film (unpaid of course) that takes place in the matrix universe - this is simply because its something that I've dreamt about doing for a long time. I also know other professionals in the industry (such as a skilled DOP/camera op) who also is very passionate about the matrix, who also owns some very pro gear and would love to get involved with a project like this too.

Is there anyone on this group that is considering making a project like this? Feel free to get in touch if you are.

Best regards

James

message.text:
… ich fragte dich, warum grad Griechenland.
Und warum das Schild in deiner Hand.
Du sagtest: „ da ist schön.“
Dahin soll die Reise gehen.

Ref. Ich fuhr mit dir nach Griechenland.
Da hinter den Bergen,
Wo ich meine große Liebe fand.

Acting headshots in Lincolnshire, East Midlands and beyond.

Hi, I'm Andrej and I'll coach and guide you in front of the camera to achieve a range of headshots that help you stand out and get noticed.

My studio is portable and I’m happy to travel to you if you'd like.

Find out more and book here:

https://www.CaptivatingHeadshots.co.uk

or feel free to message me directly here on FB.

Available for New Year’s Eve shows – Acro Bike Act

 Disponible para shows de Fin de Año – Acro Bike Act

I am available again for New Year’s Eve / Fin de Año with my 4-minute Acro Bike Act, featured at Cirque du Soleil – BAZZAR, Sydney Opera House, Madison Square Garden, and on international stages.

Currently based in Argentina, I perform worldwide for events, galas, casinos, TV productions, and premium shows.

Perfect for year-end events, galas, and high-impact moments.

items.text:
***CASTING CALL***THE FORCE***
Last chance to be a part of cinema history!!
I'm super looking forward to seeing some of you for the London Marathon finale of the film on Saturday (reminder of full details below). THIS IS THE LAST DAY OF FILMING INVOLVING SA's so come on down if you want to be a part of this historic cinematic re-creation!

Michael Watson himself will be attending!! 

NOTE TIME CHANGES AS WELL PLEASE, IT"S A MUCH SHORTER DAY!!

DATE: Saturday the 29th of November 2025

Time: 9:00 AM – 1PM (latest).
Location: St James’s Park, London SW1A 2BJ
Fee: Unpaid – your contribution will be greatly appreciated, reasonable travel expenses covered. (Water and light refreshments provided.)

2003 style mood board attached, please come in as close to the images as possible.

We’ll be recreating key moments from Michael’s marathon journey, including the start line and his triumphant finish.

ROLES NEEDED
Marathon Runners (Elite & Fun Runners)
10–14 elite-looking runners
5 fun runners
For the start line sequence, where Michael begins alongside elite athletes and shares a light-hearted moment before the race begins.
 Finish Line Crowd
40 - 50 Supporters
To create an uplifting, emotional atmosphere as Michael crosses the finish line.
(Final numbers to be confirmed by production.

email: casting@magnificentfilms.co.uk if you want to join us!
 
SEE YOU ON THE RED CARPET!!

items.text: Hello! I wondered if anyone can help, i am an actor in my graduating year at drama school looking for temporary work over christmas. I used to work in a pub all year round but i need something that i can pick up and put down due to committments of my training. what do other actors use to find work? or does anyone know any event staff/ waitressing/ bar staff agencies that are good at finding work? many thanks!

topComments.text:
My first lifesaving work I had out of drama school, once completely out of money lol, was with the hospitality company. I later moved on to twist events (they were great). 

Another thing to explore is  party entertainment, although for that you’d need a car (think that’s not the case with all agencies). I worked a few years with the party belles.

Both the above options offer full flexibility, which is perfect for performers Xo

items.text:
📣** CASTING CALL — PAID OPPORTUNITY IN CAMBRIDGE**

I'm helping a Chinese production company cast performers for a short-form Douyin (TikTok China) series filming in Cambridge UK. The project is simple, natural and focuses on everyday interactions between people from different backgrounds.

We’re looking for young male and female performers who can play natural versions of themselves — no heavy acting required.

✨ **What We’re Looking For**

Gender: Male & Female

Playing age: 20–30

Ethnicity: Caucasian

Language: Fluent English (any accent is fine, as long as it’s clear)

Comfortable acting naturally on camera

Able to follow simple scripts + light improvisation

Based in Cambridge preferred, but London/nearby areas welcome (travel covered)

**🎬 Production Details**

Location: Cambridge, UK

Usage: Douyin (China’s TikTok)

Shoot Duration: Half-day or full-day depending on the episode

Schedule: Flexible / ongoing filming

Pay: £30–£60 per hour (depending on experience)

Travel: Covered (if coming from London/nearby)

Food: Provided

Non-broadcast, social media series

📄 **About the Project**

A series of short, down-to-earth scenes showing everyday encounters between people from different backgrounds living in the UK. Performers will essentially play themselves — relaxed, natural and conversational.

**📩 How to Apply**

Please send me a DM or email me at sanan282000@gmail.com

 with:

Your name

Your age

Your location

Your headshots

A showreel (if available)

or any acting experience you have (please mention what projects or training)

Travel expenses covered*. DM me or email sanan282000@gmail.com sanan2 to apply.'

📣** CASTING CALL — PAID OPPORTUNITY IN CAMBRIDGE**

I'm helping a Chinese production company cast performers for a short-form Douyin (TikTok China) series filming in Cambridge UK. The project is simple, natural and focuses on everyday interactions between people from different backgrounds.

We’re looking for young male and female performers who can play natural versions of themselves — no heavy acting required.

✨ **What We’re Looking For**

Gender: Male & Female

Playing age: 20–30

Ethnicity: Caucasian

Language: Fluent English (any accent is fine, as long as it’s clear)

Comfortable acting naturally on camera

Able to follow simple scripts + light improvisation

Based in Cambridge preferred, but London/nearby areas welcome (travel covered)

**🎬 Production Details**

Location: Cambridge, UK

Usage: Douyin (China’s TikTok)

Shoot Duration: Half-day or full-day depending on the episode

Schedule: Flexible / ongoing filming

Pay: £30–£60 per hour (depending on experience)

Travel: Covered (if coming from London/nearby)

Food: Provided

Non-broadcast, social media series

📄 **About the Project**

A series of short, down-to-earth scenes showing everyday encounters between people from different backgrounds living in the UK. Performers will essentially play themselves — relaxed, natural and conversational.

**📩 How to Apply**

Please send me a DM or email me at sanan282000@gmail.com

 with:

Your name

Your age

Your location

Your headshots

A showreel (if available)

or any acting experience you have (please mention what projects or training)

🎬 **CASTING – POSZUKIWANA AKTORKA** 🎬

Do filmu dyplomowego realizowanego w Szkole Filmowej w Łodzi poszukujemy **aktorki w wieku 40–45 lat, Polki**, do roli opiekunki.

📍 **Projekt:** film fabularny – dyplom reżyserski
🎥 **Zdjęcia:** planowane na wiosnę/lato (dokładne terminy podamy zainteresowanym)
📌 **Rola:** Opiekunka 

**Wymagane doświadczenie aktorskie!**

Po analizie zgłoszeń wybrane osoby **zaprosimy na casting na żywo w Łodzi**.

**Zgłoszenia:**
Prosimy o przesłanie kilku słów o sobie, aktualnych zdjęć oraz, jeśli posiadasz – materiałów wideo (showreel, self tape) na adres: **[m.posiadalo@student.filmschool](mailto:m.posiadalo@student.filmschool)****.lodz.pl**

Quand j’ai créé Casting, les annonces le 3 août 2011, il m’a fallu plus d’un an pour atteindre 300 membres.

C’est dommage que l’IA de Facebook l’ait mis hors service le 7 février 2025.

Cela dit, j’ai recréé un autre groupe du même nom le 7 février 2025, mais en lettres capitales, et il compte déjà 5 938 membres   [https://www.facebook.com/groups/28380113158270311/people/...](https://www.facebook.com/groups/28380113158270311/people/?should_open_welcome_member_composer=1&locale=fr_FR&__cft__[0]=AZVmpaDAZdPWadYLon-rGPaGksDhfNljaJsyqY9VvlfMEIzp6me1BjEnJjucyEQPmny5xH_2hlYLmJkieZCU7aaJEylVDQef4Xw0S8I2mHCmtFxKGYKDin1Z-E3HYGpxa835mha_RIyi6vsa460nvniOernqUM02ud6Miw3LZsJBNA&__tn__=-UK-R). 

Les gens peuvent devenir membre dans l'ancien, mais il n'y a plus aucune nouvelle publication depuis le 7 février 2025, du coup ça ne sert à rien de devenir membre dans l'ancien groupe

sharedPost.text:
📣TURNIEJ TAŃCA w Rzeszowie!

🔥INTERNATIONAL DANCE CUP RZESZÓW 2025🔥
Pierwsza edycja. Pierwsza szansa. Pierwszy krok na scenę, która czeka właśnie na Ciebie.
Jeśli taniec to Twój żywioł — to MUSISZ być.🫵🤩
______________________
👉 SOLIŚCI & DUETY 👈

🗓️ Turniej 30.11.2025 r. - niedziela
📍 ul. Moniuszki 2 (I piętro), Centrum Rzeszowa

📩 Zgłoszenia do 23.11.2025 r.❗️
👇Link do formularza zgłoszeniowego wraz z regulaminem
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfcREPk5clGRe8_O-5lY7o-zc0YlR0Ti8_Dm4OQ2xXDWUPdXg/viewform?usp=header

📲 Nie czekaj, zgłoś się już dziś!😉 
💃TAŃCZ, TAŃCZ, TAŃCZ🕺

_________________________________
✨Kategorie taneczne & wiekowe:✨

1️⃣ Modern/ Contemporary/ Jazz/ Jazz Funk 💫
~ 10-13 lat
~ 14-17
~ 18+
-> Duety: od 10 roku życia

2️⃣ Commercial/ Hip Hop 👟
~ 10-13 lat
~ 14-17
~ 18+
-> Duety: od 10 roku życia

3️⃣ High Heels/ Latino Solo 👠
~ 16+
-> Duety: 16+
__________________

🎟️ Opłata wpisowa: 50 zł za osobę za jedną kategorię

⏳Czas prezentacji:
- Soliści: 1:30 min
- Duety: 2 min 

__________________
🔥Dlaczego warto?

→ Bo to turniej stworzony z prawdziwej pasji. Atmosfera będzie ciepła, motywująca i pełna dobrej energii.

→ Scena daje impuls. Każdy występ rozwija — a ten może dodać Ci skrzydeł.

→ Bo to idealna okazja, żeby zrobić coś dla siebie: sprawdzić się, poczuć ten moment na scenie i dać przestrzeń swojej tanecznej stronie.

→ Poznajesz nowych tancerzy i ludzi z podobnym flow, vibe-em😉 To naturalnie otwiera głowę, poszerza perspektywę i daje kontakt z osobami, które pasjonują się tym samym co Ty.

→ Łapiesz doświadczenie turniejowe bez presji przeogromnej sceny. Adrenalina, emocje, rywalizacja — ale w atmosferze, w której da się oddychać.

→ Pierwsza edycja ma swój klimat. Tego nie da się powtórzyć — jesteś częścią nowej historii🥰

__________________________________
Więcej informacji:
→ ☎️ +48 780 500 410
→ 💌 wiadomości DM
__________________________________
Graphics by Julia Widlarz 🤍

#rzeszów #rzeszow #sport #taniec #dance #szkolatanca #podkarpacie #DanceCupRzeszów2025 #TurniejTańca #TańczymyRazem #TurniejTańcaRzeszów

message.text:
‎
‎‎✨ MODEL DEVELOPMENT WORKSHOP ✨
‎Ready to own the runway with confidence, glam , uniqueness and style? 👠💪💯
‎
‎Join Coach Thony and other Runway mentors for a comprehensive model training designed to help you master:
‎💃 Runway Movement and Catwalk Mastery
‎🕴️ Posture Alignment & Stride Practice
‎🎬 Facial Expression and Attitude Training
‎📸 Mastering the Projection on Camera 
‎🎯 Practical Runway Application & Performance
‎
      
‎🕐 1 PM – 4 PM
‎📍 Victory Mall ( Activity Center ) , Balibago Sta. Rosa Laguna

Be one of our team! 
‎Enroll now — and unleash the hidden talents in you. 
‎Because your journey to greatness starts here!
‎
‎Open to aspiring models of all ages — kids, teens, and young adults who want to build their confidence and elevate their modeling skills.

Message  us or contact Ms. Joycie 09928840931 E-Mail : lagunaslearningtalentcenter@gmail.com  to secure your slot.
‎
‎
‎#LagunasTalentLearningCenter #LTA #LagunasTalentAgency #ModelDevelopmentWorkshop #VictoryMall #RunwayTraining #ModelSearch #FashionEvent #ModelWorkshop #CatwalkPerfection

items.text:
ANIMA ECLIPTICA — Sacred Small Circle (Sunday 23. November, Berlin)

A night for those who feel the call.
Shadow. Light. Truth.
A living theatre where your inner self becomes visible.

This is not a public event.
It is a protected circle, limited seats, intimate, guided with deep presence and Hands of Light.
Only for those truly ready to step into their inner portal.

Reservation is required.

🎬** Bad at Hellos Worse at Goodbyes: WORLDWIDE CASTING CALL **🇵🇭

We are urgently seeking **experienced male actors (ages 31-49)** for the upcoming project, **"Bad at Hellos Worse at Goodbyes"**! Filming will take place in the **Philippines**.

We are specifically targeting actors who hold **German, British, Czech, or American** citizenship/nationality.

**Project & Role Details**

* **Project Title:** Bad at Hellos Worse at Goodbyes
* **IMDb Link:** [https://www.imdb.com/title/tt38781319/?ref_=nv_sr_srsg_0_tt_8_nm_0_in_0_q_bad%2520at%2520hellos](https://www.imdb.com/title/tt38781319/?ref_=nv_sr_srsg_0_tt_8_nm_0_in_0_q_bad%2520at%2520hellos)
* **Filming Location:** **Philippines** (Applicants must be willing and able to travel and work in the Philippines).
* **Compensation:** **$5,000 - $7,000 USD**, based on professional credits and experience.
* **Filming dates: **February 2026 - April 2026

**Mandatory Requirements**

* **Gender/Age:** Male, strictly **31 to 49 years old**.
* **Nationality:** Must be a citizen of **Germany, the United Kingdom, the Czech Republic, or the United States**.
* **Professional Profile:** Must have an established **IMDb Profile** with verifiable credits.
* **Social Media:** Must have a minimum of **5,000+ followers** across primary social media platform(s).

**Submission Instructions**

To be considered, please email your full submission package to:

📧 **[badathellosworseatgoodbyes@gmail.com](mailto:badathellosworseatgoodbyes@gmail.com)**

**Subject Line MUST BE:** **"CASTING SUBMISSION: MALE [YOUR AGE] - [NATIONALITY] - [YOUR NAME]"**

**Your submission package must include:**
* Professional Headshot(s) and Acting Resume/CV (attached).
* A link to your Acting Reel or recent work samples.
* A direct link to your verifiable **IMDb Profile**.
* Link(s) to your main Social Media profile(s), clearly stating your current follower count.
* Your current City and Country of residence (and where you currently hold citizenship).

🚨** DEADLINE FOR SUBMISSIONS**

All materials must be received no later than **November 26th or 27th, 2025**.

*Only selected candidates meeting ****ALL**** mandatory requirements will be contacted for auditions.*

​
Wir suchen Schauspieler:innen, Darsteller:innen, Kompars:innen, Protagonist:innen und Künstler:innen aus München und Umgebung für Filme, Serien, Werbung und vieles mehr.
​
Über unsere interne Kartei vermitteln wir regelmäßig Jobs und Castings in der Schauspiel- und Medienbranche – direkt und unkompliziert.
​
👉 Der Eintrag ist kostenlos – kommentiere einfach mit “München” und erhalte den Link zur Anmeldung!

​
Wir freuen uns auf dich ❤️
Dein Castfinder-Team

**CASTING CALL — Male Actor (25–30)**

**Role:** Handler / Bodyguard / Mercenary-type

**Shoot Dates:** 30 Nov – 3 Dec (4 days)

**Location:** Guildford / Oxshott, Surrey

**Budget: **Low-budget short (collaboration)

**Expenses: **Covered up to £25/day + FOOD PROVIDED

Be part of a standout short film with an award-winning creative team who have already proven themselves on the festival circuit. We’re submitting this project to major international film festivals, backed by a full PR, distribution, and industry outreach plan designed to generate strong global exposure for cast and crew.

A great opportunity to build your showreel and join a project with exciting future ambitions. 

To apply — DM or email me with:

• a short written intro

• your showreel & headshot

• confirmation of availability for all shoot dates

 dominofilm.producer@gmail.com

✨**A pörgős karácsony előtti időszakra keresünk hostesseket és statisztákat **🎄🎄❄️

*Kötöttség nélkül végezhető kiegészítő munkalehetőség.*

* Ha szívesen keresnél egy kis extra pénzt az ünnepek előtt vagy szívesen töltenéd hasznosan a téli szünetet ,akkor  ez a lehetőség neked való: *💸💸🎁🎁

A betöltésre váró pozíciók:

- rendezvény hostess 🎈

- promóciós hostess 🎁

- szórólapos hostess📃

- közönség statiszta 🥳

- háttér statiszta 🎬

- kiemelt statiszta 🎤

A beosztást te magad írod minimum óraszám nélkül. 

Hétvégén és hétköznap egyaránt van lehetőség munkába állni.

A hostess bérek: átlagosan 2.000-2.500 Forint között mozognak óránként. 💰
A statiszta napi bérek: átlagosan 5.000-60.000 Ft között mozognak.  💰

Budapesti 15-37 éves korosztály közötti fiatalok jelentkezését várom üzenetben vagy hagyj egy 🎄 emojit a post alatt és írok neked. 📩📫

A Gold Series Production • MD & PX Films

We’re officially casting for our new Detroit emotional-drama COUCH TALK — a film about friendship, truth, healing, and the conversations that change lives.

We are looking for Detroit talent who bring real emotion, personality, and presence.

ROLES:

• Trey – Gay, feminine energy, beautiful spirit, quick with the clapbacks

• Bri – Stylish, emotional depth, loyal but conflicted

• Kenya – Strong, expressive, the heart of the group

• Demetrius – Older, smooth, grounded energy

💰 Paid Roles

🎥 Emotional Drama

👥 Detroit-Based Casting

If you’re ready to act with depth, rawness, and real Detroit soul, we want to see you.

📧 Send headshot + brief intro to:

houseofhorror40@gmail.com

Let’s make something powerful.

— Gold Series Production | MD & PX Films

items.text:
**CASTING CALL!**

Hello everyone! My name is Sofia Vargas and I’m the Producer for the UNCSA third year film, *Metanoia*. We are casting our lead characters!

Story: On the last night of Mariana’s visit to her brother Mateo in the U.S., the two Latin American siblings are pushed into unfamiliar territory when a moment of discovery at a Latin club gives Mariana a glimpse of who she truly is. Together, they navigate the fragile, unspoken shifts in identity, desire, and growing up that both pull them apart and draw them closer.

We are accepting auditions submissions! Character Breakdowns are attached. If you’re interested in auditioning for these roles, send your **name, age, pronouns,** **headshot, and role preference  **to [metanoiafilmcasting@gmail.com](mailto:metanoiafilmcasting@gmail.com) for audition materials! 

The **interest deadline **is December 1st! 

Production title: Metanoia 

Union / Non-Union: Non-Union 

Paid / Not Paid: Not Paid

Production Type: Student Film

Production Company: University of North Carolina School of the Arts (School of Filmmaking)

Director: Martín Collo Sastoque 

Producer: Sofia Vargas

Audition Type: In Person Auditions

Filming: January and February 2026

Shooting Location: Winston-Salem, NC

Email: [metanoiafilmcasting@gmail.com](mailto:metanoiafilmcasting@gmail.com)

We look forward to seeing your audition!

🎬 **CASTING CALL – “THE BIRDS ARE CHIRPING” (PAID)**

📍 **Location:** Melbourne, VIC
📅 **Casting Date:** TBC
🎥 **Shoot Type:** Short Film
💰 **Compensation:** Paid
🗣 **Language:** Slovak (Preference given to Slovak or Czech actors, though familiarity with Slavic languages is sufficient.)

A tense, atmospheric psychological short film set in Czechoslovakia, following a young woman haunted by visions of an imposing KGB spy as she searches for the truth behind her past.

**ROLES AVAILABLE**

🎭 **ZUZANNA**
*Female Presenting | 18–25*
Outspoken, rebellious, and driven by strong beliefs. Her world fractures as paranoia surrounding her father grows into a spiralling psychological descent.

🎭 **FILIP**
*Male Presenting | 40s–50s*
Worn down by years under an oppressive regime. Emotionally numb but deeply devoted to giving his daughter the freedom he never had.

🎭 **JOZEF**
*Male Presenting | 30s–50s*
A chilling, ever-present KGB spy with a disturbing confidence and sinister smile. An almost otherworldly force silently stalking the story’s edges.

**PROJECT TONE**

A moody, slow-burning psychological journey blurring memory and paranoia.
Rooted in Cold War-era tension, the film explores identity, fear, and the fragile bond between a father and daughter as reality begins to fracture.

📩 **HOW TO APPLY**

Apply via **Actors and Extras** as a **Talent PRO member with a 1-month FREE trial**:
➡️ [https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls](https://actorsandextras.com/casting-calls)

Create your free profile and get notified of new roles in your area!
Visit [https://www.actorsandextras.com](https://www.actorsandextras.com).

🔍 *This casting has been shared by Actors and Extras as a service to our talent directory members. We have received permission to share it and believe it to be legitimate. However, we strongly encourage all applicants to exercise due diligence and independently verify the details of the project before proceeding.*

Tonight and tomorrow only at No Square Theatre in Laguna Beach!

Get your tickets at: [https://www.tix.com/ticket-sales/nosquare/1804](https://www.tix.com/ticket-sales/nosquare/1804?fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAYnJpZBExdE9CMUlNdmlWaHQ1Z0hXRHNydGMGYXBwX2lkDzUxNDc3MTU2OTIyODA2MQABHhigjsOFZIS1vnXu10jY_YsHWJ5nXvz5lgiqWRc5_TvZ_pxZxMayZs6Vc-tX_aem_Qgp-5aGk8mHoi59iA-L5bQ)

SHE KILLS MONSTERS: YOUNG ADVENTURERS EDITION, a play by Qui Nguyen and directed by No Square Theatre Artistic Director, Joe Lauderdale, tells the story of high schooler Agnes Evans as she deals with the death of her younger sister, Tilly. When Agnes finds Tilly’s Dungeons & Dragons notebook, she gets pulled into an exciting adventure in the imaginary world that was her sister’s escape. The story is a thrilling, fast-paced dramatic comedy laden with homicidal fairies, nasty ogres, and ’90s pop culture celebrating both the geek and the warrior inside all of us.

November 22 & 23 Only!

🎥🎬 Warszawa Nowy Film Fabularny
🎞️ Plan historyczny rok 1964 
Data nagrań: 10.12 
Warszawa transport do i po -> Wołomin docelowo 
(10 osób dostanie kontynuację na 13.12) 
Nagrania nocne, Wołomin
Szukam Kobiet i Mężczyzn w wieku 25-40 lat jako widownia kinia.
💸 Wynagrodzenie: 150 zł netto, płatne po planie.
Szukam osób naturalnych, bez sztucznych paznokci, rzęs, o jednolitym kolorze włosów, bez makijażu  permamentnego. 
Panowie bez wygoleń,współczesnych fryzur, tatuaży w widocznych miejscach.
📩 Zgłoszenia: PAULINA@SCENERIA.COM.PL dopisek 10.12 KINO 
Imie, nazwisko, wiek, numer tel aktualne zdjęcie,gdzie dobrze widać fryzurę.

sharedPost.text:
Looking forward to delving deeper in to Making Contact with Januarys 12 week course. Applying safe yet playful approaches to build actors confidence and in physical, violent and intimate scenes. 

Participants will explore…
- Industry standards in intimacy and consent
- Mental and physical preparations for the work
- Quality boundary setting
​- Physical exploration and game play
- Contact improv and shared weight
- Exploration of theatrical violence
- Engagement in imaginary relationships under physical circumstances
- Practices in body preparation and physical/mental closure
- Final performances of fully coordinated and directed scenes.

Last places are going, but if you wish you can find out more information or put yourself on the waiting list. Check it out out…
www.bodymindvoice.co.uk￼

Bring it on 💪🏼

💻 Location: Online via Zoom

Meeting ID: 854 0409 4406

**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP  Gliwice/Katowice ( Śląsk )  **

 

   Szukam pań które nie krępują się własnego ciała i chciałaby mieć ciekawą pamiątkę w postaci klimatycznych zdjęć.  Wiem jak bardzo jest ważna akceptacja własnego ciała bo przez to też możemy inaczej funkcjonować. Przez takie zdjęcia można również tego dokonać. Sesja w głównej mierze jest jako taki motywator.

 

Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 30 **lat nie koniecznie z doświadczeniem pozowania,  na zasadach Tfp mieszkającej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposażeniu mini studio z kilkoma tłami oraz lampami. Mam również duży wybór kostiumów i gadżetów do wykorzystywania. Główny motyw do kobieta: Piękna i drapieżna! Sama sesja trwa przeważnie od 1,5h do 2h w zalezności od motywów.

** **

**Temat 1 – ‘’Kobieta mafii 1930’’**

Postać kobiety osadzona w 1930 roku w roli bogatej kobiety, która trudni się gangsterstwem. Przewidziane są ujęcia m.in. przy stoliku na którym są pieniądze, wino, rewolwer. Tło jest wydrukowane w formie muru, cegieł. Motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 2 – ‘’Wampirzyca w baroku 1700’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana najpierw w suknie czarną oraz peleryne z kapturem. Do tego czarna długa peruka oraz czarne paznokcie. W kolejnym etapie sesji motyw sensualny.

 

**Temat 3 – ‘’Duchy lasu’’**

Postać kobiety ubrana w wianek i w pelerynę z otwartym przodem. W dłoni ma zakrwawiony sierp. Usta czarne oraz paznokcie.

 

**Temat 4 – ‘’Kleopatra’’**

Postać kobiety z czarna peruką w stylu Kleopatry. W prawej recę trzymac będzie berło Anubisa a w drugiej ręcę księgę umarłych. Na biodrach będzie mieć jedynie klasyczne odzienie z 2 części. Na klatce piersiowej założony będzie napierśnik złoty.

 

https://www.maxmodels.pl/lukus_wielki2

**Zapraszam na stronę Facebook Łukasz Magiera – Fotografia**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

items.text:
Cześć! Mam na imię Tomek i pracuję przy projektach artystycznych Disneyladzie 
Obecnie przygotowuje się do przedstawienia oferty zorganizowania castingu w Polsce i szukam Waszej opinii oraz wskazówek, aby wybrać najlepsze miejsce i czas.

Będę wdzięczny za pomoc w odpowiedzi na kilka pytań:
⭐ Które miasto byłoby najlepsze na casting? Warszawa, czy może inne?
⭐ Czy znacie dobre szkoły tańca lub miejsca/sceny, które sprawdziłyby się jako lokalizacja castingu?
⭐ Czy kojarzycie Studio 42 – polecacie?
⭐ Kiedy polscy tancerze i performerzy najczęściej szukają pracy za granicą?
⭐ Gdzie najlepiej publikować ogłoszenia, aby dotrzeć do jak największej liczby tancerzy/aktorów/animatorów? Jakie grupy, portale, sieci polecacie?
items.previewDescription: Polubienia: 9678, komentarze: 86. „Po 17 latach przerwy w Polsce odbył się casting do Disneylandu – i udało mi się spełnić marzenie! 🏰✨ Już ponad miesiąc pracuję w Disneylandzie w Paryżu i jestem za to niesamowicie wdzięczny ❤️”
items.title: TikTok · _tumek_

topComments.text: Hej, myślę, że dobrym pomysłem byłoby wzięcie pod uwagę Krakowa, bo o dziwo jest ono mam wrażenie, że pomijanym miastem na tle Warszawy czy Wrocławia w tej kategorii, a posiada wiele chociażby akademii aktorskich. Chciałabym również dopytać czy jest jakaś szansa dla osób które chciałyby na przyklad pomóc przy takim projekcie, pomimo, że są amatorami? Ślicznie dziękuję

items.text:
Acting in Longer Form – with Arek Ziętek

Ready to take your acting and improv to the next level and bring real stories to life on stage? This workshop is all about longer scenes, deeper characters, and authentic storytelling, guided by Arek Ziętek, one of Warsaw’s most respected theatre improvisers and teachers.

Arek has worked with Keith Johnstone, the father of modern improvisation, and now he’s sharing that knowledge in this unique advanced workshop for experienced performers.

You’ll explore long-form improvisation techniques, learn to build emotional depth in your characters, and discover how to create stories that feel real, funny, and moving, all in English.

👉 Important: This is not for beginners. You’ll need some previous acting or improv experience and a confident level of English. We’re keeping the group small so everyone gets space, feedback, and focus.

Why join?
✨ Learn from one of Poland’s top improv teachers.
✨ Master storytelling through longer scenes and strong relationships.
✨ Work in English with passionate, international performers.
✨ Grow your stage presence and confidence in a supportive circle.

Schedule & Pricing
📆 Starting: Tuesday, November 25th
⏰ 7:00 PM
📍 Atlas Tower – al. Jerozolimskie 123A, Warsaw

🎟️ Limited Spots:
First 5 applicants: 300 PLN (full 4-week course)
Next 5 spots: 350 PLN

If more than 10 apply, we might open a second group, but no promises!

Join us for a deep, fun, and creative exploration of what it means to truly act and improvise in longer form.

Very Limited Spots https://fienta.com/pl/acting-storytelling-improv-workshop-with-arek-zietek-155700

A night for those who feel the call.
Shadow. Light. Truth.
A living theatre where your inner self becomes visible.

This is not a public event.
It is a protected circle, limited seats, intimate, guided with deep presence and Hands of Light.
Only for those truly ready to step into their inner portal.

Reservation is required.

LATEST SOUTH AFRICAN ACTION FILM SECURES MAJOR DISTRIBUTION DEAL!

Find out more here: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt33057143

items.text:
MUSICIANS WANTED – SUMMER 2026 IN GREECE

We are seeking talented solo and duo musicians to perform in our 5★ partner resorts in Greece during the Summer 2026 season (May–October).  You will be required to perform 4 sets of 45 minutes, 6 times a week.

Pianists, violinists, saxophonists, guitarists, singers, or musical duos offering elegant live performances are welcome to apply.

WE OFFER
 • 6-month contracts in luxury resorts
 • Competitive monthly salary based on experience and skills
 • Free accommodation, meals, and beverages
 • Flight reimbursement up to €300 and airport transfer

REQUIREMENTS
 • Professional solo or duo musicians ready to perform live
 • Wide and versatile repertoire (jazz, lounge, pop, classical, etc.)
 • Own instruments and performance attire (resort-appropriate style)
 • Only  EU passports !
        

APPLY NOW
Send your promo video to: 

adriano@palmera-agency.com

Du kommst aus Hamburg und Umgebung? Wir suchen dich!

​

Wir suchen Schauspieler:innen, Darsteller:innen, Kompars:innen, Protagonist:innen und Künstler:innen aus Hamburg und Umgebung für Filme, Serien, Werbung und vieles mehr.

​

Über unsere interne Kartei vermitteln wir regelmäßig Jobs und Castings in der Schauspiel- und Medienbranche – direkt und unkompliziert.

​

👉 Der Eintrag ist kostenlos – kommentiere einfach mit “HAMBURG” und erhalte den Link zur Anmeldung!

Oder kennst du jemanden, der aus der Nähe kommt? Dann markiere ihn! 

​

Wir freuen uns auf dich ❤️

Dein Castfinder-Team

Curious about acting? Or looking to reconnect with your craft before the year ends? Join us at East Van Coaching for two upcoming workshops this December:

Acting for Beginners

December 5th | 5PM–7PM

$50 + GST

A welcoming intro class for anyone wanting to explore acting, build confidence, and learn the fundamentals.

The Actor’s Mental Maintenance: Relaxation & Presence

December 13th | 10AM–1PM

$50 + GST

A grounding workshop focused on regulating the nervous system, cultivating presence, and strengthening your inner actor.

Location:

2910 Commercial Drive, Vancouver, BC

For more info or to save your spot, email us at info@eastvancoaching.com

or visit https://eastvancoaching.com/class-sign-up

See you in class!

🎬 **CASTING – POSZUKIWANA AKTORKA** 🎬

Do filmu dyplomowego realizowanego w Szkole Filmowej w Łodzi poszukujemy **aktorki w wieku ok. 30 lat, pochodzenia azjatyckiego**.

📍 **Projekt:** film fabularny – dyplom reżyserski
🎥 **Zdjęcia:** planowane na wiosnę/lato
📌 **Rola:** An – główna rola

**Wymagania:**
– **wymagane doświadczenie aktorskie**
– znajomość języka angielskiego 

Po analizie zgłoszeń wybrane osoby **zaprosimy na casting na żywo w Łodzi**.

**Zgłoszenia:**
Prosimy o przesłanie kilku słów o sobie, aktualnych zdjęć oraz, jeśli posiadasz – materiałów wideo (showreel, self tape) na adres: **[m.posiadalo@student.filmschool](mailto:m.posiadalo@student.filmschool)****.lodz.pl**

items.text:
The disconnect between the film world and the social media marketing world literally is nonsensical 😆 Film acts snooty and above content lol Social Media folks have trouble transitioning into longer form content and more polished visuals. Both need to be working together though...there is a need on both ends. 

Film teams should be using content creation to supplement income and fund projects! You know what lemme hush lol Come talk to me Sunday about how you can diversify your film business...

Palmera Job Offer S26

Ready for the best summer of your life? Join our Entertainment Teams and work under the sun in beautiful Greece. ☀️🇬🇷

WE ARE LOOKING FOR PERFORMERS:

Position: (Aerialist, Acrobat, Juggler – performing shows at various hotels)
Contract Period: 1 May – 31 October 2026
Monthly Net Salary: From €1,000 - 1500€ (depending on experience, skills, and performance)
Employment Type: Swiss contract or self-employed freelancer

Venues: 4★ and 5★ hotels located on Kos, Crete, or Rhodes Island, Greece

Terms and Benefits
 • 1–2 weeks of free rehearsals prior to the contract start date, depending on the candidate’s progress in learning choreography
 • One day off per week
 • 1–2 performances per day( 1hour show )
 • Free accommodation and board at each hotel where performances take place, including meals in the main restaurant and beverages
 • Accident, pension, and social insurance coverage included
 • €300 travel bonus reimbursed with the final salary for six-month contracts
 • Free airport transfer upon arrival in Greece
 • Free internet and laundry services
 • Work uniforms and costumes provided
 • Company car available for work-related purposes
 • Additional performance bonus available at the end of the contract
 • Potential for career growth within the company and opportunities for contract renewal
 • An exceptional opportunity to gain professional and cultural experience under the Greek sun ☀

🎥 Watch our show productions:
https://youtu.be/9PdbLO–GX4?si=W8fKURLEWPjE9bCG

📩Apply Now for Online Auditions! Make Summer 2026 unforgettable — send your CV to: adriano@palmera-agency.com

Best regards,
Palmera Team

Producer and actor perks are still available!
https://www.indiegogo.com/en/projects/talkhardcinema/american-mother-taryn-manning-noel-g-keith-coogan?ref=explore-creator-page
Grab a producer/actor perk on AMERICAN MOTHER. James Duval (INDEPENDENCE DAY, DONNIE DARKO, GONE IN 60 SECONDS, Greg Araki's TEEN APOCALYPSE trilogy) has joined the cast, alongside...
Taryn Manning (ORANGE IS THE NEW BLACK, CROSSROADS, HUSTLE & FLOW, 8 MILE, MEAN GIRLS, SONS OF ANARCHY, THE ITALIAN JOB, CLEVELAND ABDUCTION, COLD MOUNTAIN), Nichole Brown (Aisha from COBRA KAI, RAVEN'S HOME), Keith Coogan (ADVENTURES IN BABYSITTING, TOY SOLDIERS, JAY AND SILENT BOB REBOOT, DON'T TELL MOM THE BABYSITTER'S DEAD, COUSINS) and Noel G. (THE FAST AND THE FURIOUS, FURIOUS 7, TRAINING DAY, STREET KINGS, THE DARK KNIGHT RISES, HARSH TIMES, THE MULE, DRAGGED ACROSS CONCRETE).

All 5 of these actors have already wrapped, so they're definitely a part of the film (no dropping out due to scheduling conflicts, etc). Producers are currently speaking with about several more well known actors in hopes to nab at least 3 of them for the film (maybe 8-10 in total if we can get this campaign to $20k). Grab a producer and actor perk on the film at indiegogo.

And check out our other campaign for THE VICTIM, also featuring James Duval and Noel G. https://www.indiegogo.com/en/projects/talkhardcinema/the-victim?ref=explore-creator-page

Plus AMERICAN SERIAL KILLER, also featuring James Duval and with the addition of Nathan Bexton (Doug Liman's GO, and Gregg Araki's NOWHERE). Producer perks available at https://www.madsincinema.com/investors.html
